	<h1 class="title">艺术家，发ins的时候带上Gucci Logo和天竺葵印花怎么样？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-29 14:58:26 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16783/medium/16783.jpg?1446097561" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16783" data-title="《艺术家，发ins的时候带上Gucci Logo和天竺葵印花怎么样？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16783/medium/16783.jpg?1446097561" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16783.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
		<!-- 新浪微博 -->
